column3: NSLOCTEXT("", "90F614E34A1BACE22C2C3E8E5D6743B3", "How did you break free from your prison?!")
NSLOCTEXT("", "4E6CD6244E7DA84B4331FAA5AFA2896B", "Helios, listen to me. Your castle is falling apart. You need to leave with us before you get hurt.")
NSLOCTEXT("", "7EE1C43F45F8939F78C4BC95821DD936", "My castle isn\'t falling apart, it\'s been under attack by that stupid ocean outside!")
NSLOCTEXT("", "05CF622449D3CB8E31046E99854D7D7F", "Whatever, either way this place is coming down! We need to leave!")
NSLOCTEXT("", "D967680A4AE45F4FE8E0BDB5F30A7EDE", "Even if it is crumbling I can\'t leave yet. I\'m waiting for my sister to find me.")
NSLOCTEXT("", "F2BC30094072FB62DBE154BDFE34BF5F", "And if I leave the ocean will tear my castle down!")
NSLOCTEXT("", "820A38CC498F19F3B069EE9608523798", "We\'ll help you find your sister! Just come with us to somewhere safe first. Trust us!")
NSLOCTEXT("", "7FCC453745E80CE2AA937AB350A9658D", "There\'s no way your sister is going to find you here! You would have seen her by now, so come on! We\'ll go find her instead!")
NSLOCTEXT("", "BB2E1E26488C2C5CCE28DF9656DF7D2C", "Not to mention the ocean isn\'t even close to your dumb castle.")
NSLOCTEXT("", "DCB2190F4FB01F491F67DD84C7C75DA6", "Come on! We have to go!")
NSLOCTEXT("", "F77D018949295FF7303491A67F1B3C4B", "How are we gonna get out of here if it\'s all falling apart?")
NSLOCTEXT("", "DBB901B1422322BFEDB6FDBCAD5D9E4A", "Psh! Every king has a secret passage!")
